{ lib, buildRosPackage, fetchurl, ament-cmake, ament-cmake-gmock, control-msgs, fmt, hardware-interface, lifecycle-msgs, pluginlib, rclcpp-lifecycle, ros2-control-cmake, ros2-control-test-assets }:
